name: WOOF
description: WOOF is here to dominate Solana, not just as another token but as a force of nature. We’re here to clear out the weak, eliminate the noise, and make way for the true rulers of the blockchain—dog tokens. The era of uncertainty and hesitation is over. This is the dawn of a new age, where only the strongest survive, and WOOF is leading the charge. We’re not just another project lost in the sea of mediocrity; we are the growl that echoes through every corner of the blockchain. We strike fear into the hearts of our rivals, marking our territory with every transaction, every movement, and every innovation. The days of weak hands and feeble attempts at dominance are numbered. The pack is assembling, stronger than ever, driven by an unshakable vision: total domination of Solana.
